OL,4,CAmerican sweets posing 'serious health
OL,5,Crisks'
OL,7,FStaffordshire Trading Standards are
OL,8,Fwarning that imported American sweets
OL,9,Fand snacks are posing "serious health
OL,10,Frisks to children".
OL,12,FThese brightly coloured sweets, snacks
OL,13,Fand drinks are heavily promoted by
OL,14,Fsocial media influencers, where viral
OL,15,Fvideos show 'candy hauls' and taste
OL,16,Ftests of imported products.
