OL,7,FWhilst these products are legal in the
OL,8,FUS they don't meet don't meet UK
OL,9,Fsafety and legal standards. Many don't
OL,10,Fhave proper allergen warnings and
OL,11,Fcontain illegal additives with known
OL,12,Fhealth risks or were expired.
OL,14,FA recent pilot and work from
OL,15,FStaffordshire Trading Standards team
OL,16,Fhas confiscated more than 7,000 non-
OL,17,Fcompliant products valued at around
OL,18,Falmost #20,000.
OL,20,FSome of these illegal additives
OL,21,Fthey've identified are:
