OL,7,FDean Cooke, CTSI Lead Officer for
OL,8,FFood, explained:
OL,10,F"Social media has amplified the demand
OL,11,Ffor American sweets, with influencers
OL,12,Fon platforms like TikTok showcasing
OL,13,Fthese colourful products in ways that
OL,14,Fappeal to children and teenagers.
OL,15,FWhile this drives seasonal sales, it
OL,16,Falso creates a dangerous market for
OL,17,Fitems that fail to meet UK safety
OL,18,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
