OL,7,FCouncillor Victoria Wilson, Cabinet
OL,8,FMember with responsibility for Trading
OL,9,FStandards at Staffordshire County
OL,10,FCouncil, added:
OL,12,F"Our Trading Standards team works
OL,13,Ftirelessly to ensure that food sold in
OL,14,FStaffordshire complies with safety
OL,15,Fstandards. During this pilot project,
OL,16,Fwe were alarmed to find over 3,300
OL,17,Funsafe items on sale, many of which
OL,18,Fcontained unauthorised ingredients and
OL,19,Fwere targeted at children.
