OL,7,F"These items are often poorly labelled
OL,8,Fand can contain harmful additives,
OL,9,Fposing serious public health concerns.
OL,10,FParents need to stay alert and avoid
OL,11,Fproducts with unclear labelling,
OL,12,Fespecially during the festive season."
